she's comin' outta the gate.

1492
01:35:38,572 --> 01:35:41,658
The filly's nervous.
Never a winner on this track.

1493
01:35:43,410 --> 01:35:46,496
Take your pitch
and swing, baby.

1494
01:35:46,580 --> 01:35:48,165
I do.

1495
01:35:48,248 --> 01:35:52,669
With the power vested in me,
I pronounce you man and wife.

1496
01:35:52,753 --> 01:35:55,631
You may kiss
the bride.

1497
01:35:56,590 --> 01:35:59,343
This is the
happiest day of my life.

1498
01:36:01,053 --> 01:36:03,764
I always love these days,
too, Charley.

1499
01:36:03,847 --> 01:36:05,766
I really do.

1500
01:36:05,849 --> 01:36:09,102
Hey, atta boy,
Charley.

1501
01:36:13,857 --> 01:36:16,485
The greatest comeback
in marital history.

1502
01:36:16,568 --> 01:36:18,654
- Good luck, babe.
- Thank you.

1503
01:36:18,737 --> 01:36:21,323
After Sherry and I get married,
we're gonna get divorced.

1504
01:36:21,406 --> 01:36:23,367
- This is so romantic.
- No.

1505
01:36:29,915 --> 01:36:33,168
[Phil] And so the happy newly,
newly, newlyweds...

1506
01:36:33,252 --> 01:36:35,212
