1507
01:36:35,254 --> 01:36:38,674
where, you would imagine,
they lived happily-ever-after.

1508
01:36:38,715 --> 01:36:43,178
Truth? They drove straight to a walnut
grove in Culver City, California.

1509
01:36:43,262 --> 01:36:46,807
See, for the first time in his life,
Charley had plans.

1510
01:36:46,890 --> 01:36:49,226
This is it.

1511
01:36:50,644 --> 01:36:53,564
This is what?

1512
01:36:53,605 --> 01:36:56,400
This is ours.
26 acres.

1513
01:36:56,483 --> 01:37:00,195
I bought it. It'll be
finished in nine months.

1514
01:37:00,279 --> 01:37:05,576
- Charley, not another big house.
- Not a house.

1515
01:37:05,659 --> 01:37:09,913
A movie studio.
Pearl Productions.

1516
01:37:09,997 --> 01:37:13,500
I'm gonna make movies
just for you, baby!

1517
01:37:13,584 --> 01:37:15,711
Oh, Charley...

1518
01:37:15,794 --> 01:37:18,881
- what do you know about making movies?
- What's to know?

1519
01:37:18,922 --> 01:37:21,717
You buy a movie camera.
I point the camera at you...

1520
01:37:21,800 --> 01:37:24,553
and America falls
in love with you...

1521
01:37:24,595 --> 01:37:27,598
just the way I did.

1522
01:37:27,639 --> 01:37:30,601
[Phil]
Pearl Studios cost 15 million bucks.

1523
01:37:30,684 --> 01:37:33,395
Lucky coincidence.
That's all the money Charley had left.

1524
01:37:33,437 --> 01:37:37,191
Nine months later,
a star was about to be born.

1525
01:37:37,274 --> 01:37:40,277
Except...
it came out a baby.

1526
01:37:42,654 --> 01:37:44,615
Unbelievable.

1527
01:37:47,618 --> 01:37:50,370
But it didn't stop production,
no siree.

1528
01:37:50,454 --> 01:37:53,540
Because with hard work
and perseverance...

1529
01:37:53,624 --> 01:37:56,543
11 months later
they had another baby.

1530
01:37:56,627 --> 01:37:59,129
Finally, Charley found
the right property for Vicki:

1531
01:37:59,213 --> 01:38:01,715
A big-budget
musical extravaganza.

1532
01:38:01,798 --> 01:38:03,759
When Vicki heard the news,
she was so excited...

1533
01:38:03,800 --> 01:38:05,385
she had twins.

1534
01:38:05,469 --> 01:38:08,222
Charley was never happier
in his life.

1535
01:38:08,305 --> 01:38:11,391
He had Vicki,
a family, a home.

1536
01:38:11,475 --> 01:38:14,603
Only he didn't have the studio,
which went bankrupt.

1537
01:38:14,645 --> 01:38:16,772
There's an old saying
in Hollywood...

1538
01:38:16,855 --> 01:38:19,066
"You can't make hits
unless you make pictures. "

1539
01:38:19,149 --> 01:38:22,486
Vicki got back
to her singing...

1540
