and burned.

1550
01:39:00,023 --> 01:39:04,486
1954 found the rest of us
riding the tail of a comet.

1551
01:39:04,570 --> 01:39:07,656
Tony and me were starring
with "La Hayworth."

1552
01:39:07,739 --> 01:39:09,992
Sammy had a hit musical
on Broadway.

1553
01:39:10,075 --> 01:39:13,287
And George had Cincinnati
in second place.

1554
01:39:13,370 --> 01:39:16,999
About a year passed,
and another of our brave comrades fell.

1555
01:39:17,082 --> 01:39:20,043
Tony Madden,
now MGM's biggest star...

1556
01:39:20,085 --> 01:39:24,673
