web that traps us all...marriage.

1557
01:39:24,756 --> 01:39:28,135
He not only got the girl,
he bought Lew Horner's house.

1558
01:39:28,218 --> 01:39:31,346
I'm telling ya, irony,
irony everywhere.

1559
01:39:31,430 --> 01:39:35,392
I wonder if she knows
it's a toupee.

1560
01:39:35,434 --> 01:39:39,396
- That's not his real hair?
- It is, but when it fell out...

1561
01:39:39,438 --> 01:39:41,690
he had it made
into a toupee.

1562
01:39:41,773 --> 01:39:45,819
- Look at these fool guys.
- That's us seven years ago.

1563
01:39:45,903 --> 01:39:48,363
Do you think they'll
make it as big as we did?

1564
01:39:48,405 --> 01:39:50,407
Nah, we're the last
of our breed.

1565
01:39:50,449 --> 01:39:53,202
Isn't one of your friends
missing, darling?

1566
01:39:53,243 --> 01:39:55,412
Charley Pearl and Vicki.

1567
01:39:55,495 --> 01:39:58,540
- They'll be here. Don't worry.
- I hope nothing's wrong.

1568
01:39:58,624 --> 01:40:01,376
Nah! Probably just stopped
off to have another kid.

1569
01:40:01,418 --> 01:40:06,882
Sorry I couldn't buy you
a new dress for the party.

1570
01:40:06,924 --> 01:40:12,054
Charley, I've only had this
a year and I've worn it twice.

1571
01:40:12,095 --> 01:40:15,224
I never thought a wife of mine
would wear costume jewelery.

1572
01:40:15,307 --> 01:40:18,393
It's not even good
costume jewelery.

1573
01:40:18,435 --> 01:40:22,189
You don't like this bracelet?
I love it!

1574
01:40:22,272 --> 01:40:25,442
Who cares? It looks better
than the real stuff anyway.

1575
01:40:28,278 --> 01:40:30,405
Let's not go.

1576
01:40:30,447 --> 01:40:34,034
It's gonna be boring,
the same jokes, songs...

1577
01:40:34,117 --> 01:40:37,621
the same faces.
I'm sick of these people.

1578
01:40:37,704 --> 01:40:41,625
These guys were more laughs
when they were bums.

1579
01:40:43,335 --> 01:40:46,880
We've missed the
last three parties.

1580
01:40:46,964 --> 01:40:49,883
You've gotta stop hiding
from your friends, Charley.

1581
01:40:49,967 --> 01:40:54,555
- They're your friends.
- I'm not hiding from my friends.

1582
01:40:57,641 --> 01:41:00,227
Okay. Never mind.
Let's go.

1583
01:41:00,310 --> 01:41:04,773
Wait, what did you mean,
"hiding from my friends"?

1584
01:41:04,857 --> 01:41:08,735
- Never mind!
- Hey, I want an answer to my question.

1585
01:41:08,819 --> 01:41:11,321
- Just let go of it.
- What did you mean?

1586
01:41:11,405 --> 01:41:15,117
- What did you mean by that?
- It doesn't matter, Charley!

1587
01:41:19,830 --> 01:41:22,457
You just...

1588
01:41:22,541 --> 01:41:25,627
you just had a little
run of bad luck.

1589
01:41:25,711 --> 01:41:27,963
"A run of bad luck"?

1590
01:41:28,005 --> 01:41:31,258
I've had a fucking marathon!

1591
01:41:31,341 --> 01:41:34,845
- Why don't you go to
the party by yourself?
- No.

1592
01:41:34,928 --> 01:41:37,514
There'll be a lot
of successful people like you.

1593
01:41:37,598 --> 01:41:40,309
You can compare your reviews
in "Variety,"

1594
