how many times your names
have been in the columns.

1595
01:41:44,688 --> 01:41:46,690
Okay?

1596
01:41:46,773 --> 01:41:49,860
I didn't ask you to build
the studio, Charley.

1597
01:41:49,943 --> 01:41:52,029
I didn't say
"Make me a movie star."

1598
01:41:52,112 --> 01:41:54,531
I just wanted to sing,
that's all!

1599
