I pulled you out of that place
in Vegas, didn't I?

1607
01:42:21,767 --> 01:42:24,728
You're never gonna let me
forget, are you?

1608
01:42:24,770 --> 01:42:28,857
How you pulled me out of Vegas
and made me respectable.

1609
01:42:28,899 --> 01:42:32,361
Then I work my ass off,
gain a little self-respect
while bringing up your kids.

1610
01:42:32,402 --> 01:42:35,239
But you can't take that,
can you, Charley?

1611
01:42:36,573 --> 01:42:40,244
What do you want?
Me to stay at home?

1612
01:42:40,327 --> 01:42:42,663
I can be a wife!
I can be a bimbo!

1613
01:42:42,746 --> 01:42:45,082
It's your choice.
What do you want?

1614
01:42:45,123 --> 01:42:48,877
No, no, no.
I'm the bimbo here.

1615
01:42:48,961 --> 01:42:51,922
I mean,
I'm a kept man.

1616
01:42:51,964 --> 01:42:54,007
- No, Charley.
- Do you know where this party is?

1617
01:42:54,091 --> 01:42:58,095
This is in the house
that Adele Horner lived in...

1618
01:42:58,178 --> 01:43:01,557
- a place where I was treated
like a king once.
- It doesn't matter.

1619
01:43:01,598 --> 01:43:05,060
There are waiters making
more money at this party...

1620
01:43:05,102 --> 01:43:07,521
